// Session Store
// Zustand store for managing all session-scoped state: sessions, diagrams, documents,
// designs, spreadsheets, snippets, todos, collab state, and selection.

State shape:
  sessions: Session[]
  currentSession: Session | null
  isLoading, error
  diagrams: Diagram[]  selectedDiagramId: string | null
  documents: Document[]  selectedDocumentId: string | null
  designs: Design[]  selectedDesignId: string | null
  spreadsheets: Spreadsheet[]  selectedSpreadsheetId: string | null
  snippets: Snippet[]  selectedSnippetId: string | null
  taskGraphSelected: boolean
  todos: ProjectTodo[]  todosSelected: boolean  todosProject: string | null  selectedTodoId: number | null
  collabState: CollabState | null
  pendingDiff: DiffState | null

Only one artifact type can be selected at a time: selecting a diagram clears all other selection fields, and vice versa.

FUNCTION setSessions(sessions)                                          EXPORT
  Replace the full sessions list.

---

FUNCTION setCurrentSession(session)                                     EXPORT
  IF the new session matches the current one (same project + name), do nothing.
  ELSE clear all artifact lists, selections, and collab state, then set the new session.

---

FUNCTION setLoading(loading)                                            EXPORT
FUNCTION setError(error)                                                EXPORT

---

FUNCTION setDiagrams(diagrams)                                          EXPORT
  Replace diagrams list. IF the currently selected diagram is no longer in the list, clear selectedDiagramId.

---

FUNCTION addDiagram(diagram)                                            EXPORT
  Append diagram if it isn't already in the list (deduplication by ID).

---

FUNCTION updateDiagram(id, updates)                                     EXPORT
  Merge updates into the diagram with the matching ID.

---

FUNCTION removeDiagram(id)                                              EXPORT
  Remove the diagram. IF it was selected, clear selectedDiagramId.

---

FUNCTION selectDiagram(id)                                              EXPORT
  IF the diagram exists (or id is null), set selectedDiagramId and clear all other selections.

---

FUNCTION getSelectedDiagram() -> Diagram | undefined                    EXPORT
  Return the diagram matching selectedDiagramId.

---

FUNCTION setDocuments / addDocument / updateDocument / removeDocument / selectDocument / getSelectedDocument
  Same pattern as diagram equivalents above.                            EXPORT

---

FUNCTION setDesigns / addDesign / updateDesign / removeDesign / selectDesign / getSelectedDesign
  Same pattern as diagram equivalents above.                            EXPORT

---

FUNCTION setSpreadsheets / addSpreadsheet / updateSpreadsheet / removeSpreadsheet / selectSpreadsheet / getSelectedSpreadsheet
  Same pattern as diagram equivalents above.                            EXPORT

---

FUNCTION setSnippets / addSnippet / updateSnippet / removeSnippet / selectSnippet / getSelectedSnippet
  Same pattern as diagram equivalents above.                            EXPORT

---

FUNCTION setCollabState(state)                                          EXPORT
  Set collabState.

---

FUNCTION selectTaskGraph()                                              EXPORT
  Set taskGraphSelected = true and clear all artifact selections.

---

FUNCTION clearTaskGraphSelection()                                      EXPORT
  Set taskGraphSelected = false.

---

FUNCTION setTodos(todos)                                                EXPORT
FUNCTION addTodo(todo)                                                  EXPORT
FUNCTION removeTodo(id)                                                 EXPORT
  Standard list management for project todos.

---

FUNCTION selectTodos(project)                                           EXPORT
  Enter todos view: set todosSelected = true, store the project, clear all session/artifact state.

---

FUNCTION selectTodo(id)                                                 EXPORT
  IF id is null, clear todo selection and session state.
  ELSE find the matching todo and set currentSession to { project: todosProject, name: todo.sessionName },
  clearing all artifact selections and collab state.

---

FUNCTION updateStoreTodo(id, updates)                                   EXPORT
  Merge updates into the matching todo.

---

FUNCTION setPendingDiff(diff)                                           EXPORT
FUNCTION clearPendingDiff()                                             EXPORT
  Store or clear a pending document diff (used to highlight recent patches in the editor).

---

FUNCTION clearSession()                                                 EXPORT
  Clear currentSession, all artifact lists and selections, todos, collab state, and error.

---

FUNCTION reset()                                                        EXPORT
  Reset entire store to initial state.
